flowchart TD
    START([Encountering a skeleton field])

    T1{Test 1:<br/>structural source<br/>verify ได้ใน BIBLE memory?}
    T2{Test 2:<br/>derivation rule<br/>อธิบายเป็น 1 ปย. ได้?}
    T3{Test 3:<br/>trace ค่าทุก field<br/>กลับมาได้?}
    T4{Test 4:<br/>status flag user refines<br/>+ _derivation_method?}

    FILL([✅ FILL])
    SKIP1([❌ skip, ask user])
    SKIP2([❌ skip])
    SKIP3([❌ skip])
    SKIP4([❌ skip])

    START --> T1
    T1 -- no --> SKIP1
    T1 -- yes --> T2
    T2 -- no --> SKIP2
    T2 -- yes --> T3
    T3 -- no --> SKIP3
    T3 -- yes --> T4
    T4 -- no --> SKIP4
    T4 -- yes --> FILL

    style FILL fill:#d4edda,stroke:#155724,stroke-width:3px
    style SKIP1 fill:#f8d7da
    style SKIP2 fill:#f8d7da
    style SKIP3 fill:#f8d7da
    style SKIP4 fill:#f8d7da
